## 1. Methodology

### Design
- **Baseline**: Legacy mode (all overrides OFF) vs Full Override (all 26 points ON)
- **9 logical groups** tested independently (only that group's points enabled, all others disabled)
- Each group tested on the **same data** with the same seed for fair comparison
- Position sizing: `vol_adjusted` (conservative, caps all positions regardless of confidence)

